  "title": "QAQC Engineer #81473",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Construction</li><li>Position Title: <strong>QAQC Engineer</strong></li><li>Working Location: Jurong/Islandwide</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days (Mon - Fri 8.00am - 6.00pm; Sat 8.00am - 12.00pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic salary up to $6,000 + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Experience in auditing</li><li>Familiar with Architectural and Structural trade</li><li>Conduct pre-inspection of work prior to joint inspection with BCA</li><li>Prepare request for inspection for the project</li><li>Compile and submit QAQC documents or records to the client</li><li>Liaise with the client in any issues concerning quality control of the project</li><li>Review and inspect all inspection reports for compliance</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma / Degree in Quality Assurance Engineering or other related field</li><li>Minimum 3 years of relevant experience in a QAQC role within the building construction industry</li><li>CONQUAS Manager Certificate</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#81473 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
